name: Mulgowie Cleaned & Cut Green Beans With A Balsamic Dressing Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Place green beans in the microwave following the on-pack guidelines.
Microwave for 5 minutes. Be careful when removing from microwave as these will be hot.
Drizzle with balsamic dressing when hot. Allow to cool until warm enough to eat.
